  "detailed_description": "Dice & Dungeons is a unique deck builder. You build a DICE deck (dicebuilding)! Explore dungeons, fight enemies with increasingly difficult and get new dice to your deck. A dungeon and it's challenges are never the same as before.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Based on dice building board games<br />\r\n- Several different dice to build your \"deck\"<br />\r\n- RPG elements<br />\r\n- Character classes<br />\r\n- Weapons and other items<br />\r\n- Unique experience of building dice decks<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*This game is not easy. You need build a good deck of dice and have a good strategy to win",
  "about_the_game": "Dice & Dungeons is a unique deck builder. You build a DICE deck (dicebuilding)! Explore dungeons, fight enemies with increasingly difficult and get new dice to your deck. A dungeon and it's challenges are never the same as before.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Based on dice building board games<br />\r\n- Several different dice to build your \"deck\"<br />\r\n- RPG elements<br />\r\n- Character classes<br />\r\n- Weapons and other items<br />\r\n- Unique experience of building dice decks<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*This game is not easy. You need build a good deck of dice and have a good strategy to win",
